(53,	1,	'2022-10-25 06:44:12',	'2022-10-25 06:44:12',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>History’s greatest warriors brawl to prove who’s the best in an epic test of strength and skill. These slugfests are salted with powerful weapons and gadgets. Every weapon you pick up changes your style of play</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Brawlhalla is a free 2D platform fighting game that supports up to 8 local or online players with full cross-play for PC, Xbox One, Xbox Series X, PS5, PS4, iOS, Nintendo Switch, and Android.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Online Ranked 1v1</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Climb the ranked ladder from Tin up to Platinum and beyond! Matches you against players near your skill level.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Online Ranked 2v2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Climb the ranked ladder with a friend! Matches you and a partner against teams near you skill level. Your friend can be online or right next to you</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4 Player Online Free for All</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Casual matches where four fighters enter, but only one can win.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Cross-play Custom Rooms&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Invite up to 8 friends on PC, MacOS, Xbox One, Xbox Series X, PS5, PS4, iOS, Nintendo Switch, and Android or locally to a huge variety of custom matches: 4v4s, 1v3, 2v2, FFA, and much more.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Many Game Modes</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Mix things up with Brawlball, Bombsketball, Capture the Flag, Kung-Foot, and many more fun party game modes.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The Training Room&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Practice combos and setups inside the Training Room! Look at detailed frame data, hitboxes, hurtboxes, and sharpen your skills.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Local Custom Teams</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Team-up on your local machine, by adding up to 4 bots into the mix for living-room level mayhem.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Local Single Player</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Square off against bots in a three game tournament series. Perfect for warmups or score grinders.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->',	'Brawlhalla',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'brawlhalla',	'',	'',	'2022-10-26 06:51:51',	'2022-10-26 06:51:51',	'',	0,	'http://wpalessandro.local/?p=53',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
